flowchart TD
    A[业务接口<br/>WHERE + ORDER BY + LIMIT + 返回列] --> B[索引契约<br/>tenant_id, status, created_at DESC, id DESC]
    B --> C[Planner 比较候选路径]

    C -->|少量行/可早停| D[Index / Backward Index Scan]
    C -->|列齐全且 VM 可见| E[Index Only Scan]
    C -->|中等比例、TID 分散| F[Bitmap Index + Bitmap Heap Scan]
    C -->|大范围| G[Seq Scan]

    D --> H[Meta → Root → Internal → Leaf]
    E --> H
    F --> H
    H --> I[Index Tuple / Posting List → Heap TID]
    I -->|普通扫描| J[Heap Fetch + Snapshot 可见性]
    I -->|VM all-visible| K[直接返回索引列]

    L[INSERT / 非 HOT UPDATE / DELETE 清理] --> M[修改 Leaf]
    M -->|空间足够| N[写入索引项]
    M -->|空间不足| O[删除可回收项 / Dedup / Page Split]
    O --> P[父页 Downlink；必要时 Root Split]
    N --> Q[WAL + Dirty Buffer]
    P --> Q

    Q --> R[Primary 提交与 Checkpoint]
    Q --> S[物理副本重放]
    S --> T[Failover 后新 Primary]
    T --> U[冷 shared_buffers / OS Page Cache]
    U --> C
